<section id="problem" class="py-24 sm:py-32">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16" data-reveal>
      <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-3xl sm:text-4xl mb-4">
        AI Agents Are Powerful. <span class="text-text-muted">But Chaotic.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-text-secondary max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Without structure, session 50 looks exactly like session 1. SLOPE is designed around the three constraints that make AI agents unreliable at scale.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Three problems (compact) -->
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-16" data-stagger>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-red-900/30 bg-bg-surface p-5">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
          <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-red-400/60 shrink-0"></span>
          <h3 class="text-text-primary font-heading font-bold text-base">Context loss</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Agents crash, compact, and restart from zero. Everything they learned last session is gone.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-red-900/30 bg-bg-surface p-5">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
          <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-red-400/60 shrink-0"></span>
          <h3 class="text-text-primary font-heading font-bold text-base">No consistency</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Every session is ad-hoc. Quality depends on luck, not process. The agent might check tests, might not.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-red-900/30 bg-bg-surface p-5">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
          <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-red-400/60 shrink-0"></span>
          <h3 class="text-text-primary font-heading font-bold text-base">No improvement</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Same mistakes, same blind spots, no trends. No data to tell you if things are getting better or worse.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- The Loop -->
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto" data-reveal>
      <p class="text-emerald text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 text-center">How SLOPE Solves This</p>

      <div class="rounded-xl border border-emerald/20 bg-bg-surface p-6 sm:p-8">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <!-- PLAN -->
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-bg-card p-4">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1.5">
              <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-emerald/10 text-emerald font-heading font-bold text-[10px] shrink-0">1</span>
              <h4 class="text-emerald font-heading font-bold text-sm">Plan</h4>
            </div>
            <p class="text-text-muted text-xs leading-relaxed">Briefing reads from disk â€” scorecards, hazard maps, codebase context. The agent starts informed, not blank.</p>
            <p class="text-emerald/60 text-[10px] font-mono mt-2">solves: context loss</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Arrow -->
          <div class="flex justify-center">
            <svg width="10" height="16" class="text-emerald/40" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5,0 L5,10 L1,6 M5,10 L9,6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
          </div>

          <!-- EXECUTE -->
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-bg-card p-4">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1.5">
              <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-emerald/10 text-emerald font-heading font-bold text-[10px] shrink-0">2</span>
              <h4 class="text-emerald font-heading font-bold text-sm">Execute</h4>
            </div>
            <p class="text-text-muted text-xs leading-relaxed">Fixed routines at every stage. Same steps, same order. Automated guards catch common mistakes before they land.</p>
            <p class="text-emerald/60 text-[10px] font-mono mt-2">solves: inconsistency</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Arrow -->
          <div class="flex justify-center">
            <svg width="10" height="16" class="text-emerald/40" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5,0 L5,10 L1,6 M5,10 L9,6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
          </div>

          <!-- SCORE + LEARN -->
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-bg-card p-4">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1.5">
              <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-emerald/10 text-emerald font-heading font-bold text-[10px] shrink-0">3</span>
              <h4 class="text-emerald font-heading font-bold text-sm">Score + Learn</h4>
            </div>
            <p class="text-text-muted text-xs leading-relaxed">Every sprint produces a scorecard. Rolling stats build a performance index. Miss patterns and hazard maps feed back into the next Plan.</p>
            <p class="text-emerald/60 text-[10px] font-mono mt-2">solves: no improvement</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Loop-back -->
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-emerald/40">
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M17 1l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              <path d="M3 11V9a4 4 0 014-4h14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              <path d="M7 23l-4-4 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              <path d="M21 13v2a4 4 0 01-4 4H3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-[10px] font-mono">loops back to Plan</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-center text-text-muted text-sm mt-6">
        Sprint 1 plans blind. Sprint 50 plans with 49 sprints of structured data.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
